00:25:37,867 --> 00:25:39,268
that you knew wasn't working,

514
00:25:39,328 --> 00:25:40,988
but refused to vet with someone outside yourself

515
00:25:41,068 --> 00:25:41,528
or your team?

516
00:25:42,848 --> 00:25:45,049
How much time did you waste avoiding the inevitable?

517
00:25:45,629 --> 00:25:49,310
You need a mentor or 10 to help you vet your work

518
00:25:49,350 --> 00:25:50,610
before you waste months of resources.

