00:26:39,336 --> 00:26:40,417
before things go too far.

537
00:26:41,138 --> 00:26:42,879
Mentors can also provide an outside perspective

538
00:26:42,919 --> 00:26:45,220
for team members to keep development teams clean.

539
00:26:45,561 --> 00:26:47,442
With workflow struggles, miscommunications,

540
00:26:47,482 --> 00:26:49,023
design decisions, honest assessment

